{"tid":687472,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"受壓祭旗者下場？","createTime":"2018-06-02T09:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T15:56:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed2f4c3fbbf6cc2dfe083ec3a9cf3bbbf4fae83","tid":687472,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180602/20408402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408402&d=xD%2BGrjRUql2tyaiMwagBQU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a7f73908\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F20408402&h=126644ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20180602/20408402</a><br />\n<br />\n受壓祭旗者下場？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180602/large/e8904a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180602%2Flarge%2Fe8904a.jpg&h=292ace61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n坊間竟有以「奇女子」來形容那位法庭拍照的「唐氏綜合女」，實在侮辱了這詞兒。只是個低能失手發爛渣的廢諜，港人不大關心──世上最關心她的應是林鄭，林鄭「受天主感召選特首」，唐氏女無交5萬元保釋金虛報住址還「跟Jesus交談祂說拍照只是小事」，法律不容耶穌准許？<br />\n<br />\n笑得我。所以她倆是偽教徒，姊妹淘，探監時可一起祈禱。<br />\n<br />\n至於臘髮會馬逢國，則恃勢以權謀私，為了面子和特權，只是丁點的髮Gel令其cheap精現形吧。港人也不關心──只想知那受壓放行的機場保安下場如何？<br />\n<br />\n空總發聲明，對馬堪比689「行李門事件」的「失格」行為強烈譴責；演藝校友會發聲明，斥馬「失德」；各界均口誅筆伐&hellip;&hellip;但建制奴才護短，馬再失格失德也無事，反而那意志不堅慘遭祭旗的保安確實做錯，但當日放又死不放又死，面對的是秋後算帳抑或紀律處分？暗炒抑或明炒？我們不知──但現今狀況一定要報道。<br />\n<br />\n一個巴掌拍不響，違反航空安全禁令的是二人，正如貪污和受賄、妓女和嫖客、賤男和小三、違禁和放行&hellip;&hellip;應一視同仁懲處才是「公平」，記者們應跟進累人祭旗的肇事者馬Gel頭，以防受恐怖份子青睞收買，而我們以後千萬別與馬同一班機，危險又眼冤。  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n名貴手錶斷市 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n論極都有 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"85654b22fcd4fd89cf9f29bd5c08033768eeb66a","tid":687472,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"馬gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aee29a24bf51c14ec73ada6b2ca509d7c6cf53f","tid":687472,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85654b22fcd4fd89cf9f29bd5c08033768eeb66a","tid":687472,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:15.000Z","msg":"馬gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}